Módulo reutilizável:

```hcl
# modules/database/main.tf
variable "db_name" { type = string }
variable "cpu_core_count" { type = number }

resource "oci_database_autonomous_database" "this" {
  compartment_id         = var.compartment_ocid
  display_name           = var.db_name
  db_name                = replace(var.db_name, "-", "_")
  cpu_core_count         = var.cpu_core_count
  data_storage_size_in_tbs = var.storage_tbs
  admin_password         = random_password.admin.result
  db_workload            = var.workload
}

resource "random_password" "admin" { length = 16; special = true }

output "id" { value = oci_database_autonomous_database.this.id }
output "connection_string" { value = oci_database_autonomous_database.this.connection_strings[0].high }
```

**Use:**
```hcl
module "prod_db" {
  source         = "./modules/database"
  db_name        = "prod-database"
  cpu_core_count = 4
}
```

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs
